params.uuid: The uuid of the execution to retrieve the promptId for.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

getPromptId(bytes32).notice: Retrieves the promptId of an execution by its uuid.
